They are well-known skitmakers. But they are also into music. Here are five Nigerian skitmakers who are also musicians:   1. Broda Shaggi Multi talented skit maker Broda Shaggi does not only cracks jokes but also develop a keen interest in music. He has featured some credible talented artist in the industry. He has dropped some hit banger which featured Falz (The Bad Guy) and Zlatan Ibile. He is signed into Dvpper Music.   2. Taomaa Popular influencer, comedian Taomaa as professionally called by peers and fans do not engage in skit making comedy alone but also do some good music on the line.     Nigerian Idol 7: Gerald fails to make top 9     M.I Abaga announces engagement to Eniola Mafe     Five artists that may make history at 64th Grammys   3. Ogb_recent He is one of the fast growing comedians, content creators who has taken the social media space. He is known as a all round entertainer who will drop your jaw with hillarious skit anytime. His recent single titled “Abi you wan collect” has shows the versatality of the young entertainer   4. Emma OMG Emma OhMaGod rose to fame with music comedy and he has been consistent in dishing out music comedy contents to his fans year-in-year-out. Emma is musically gifted that he could create a drama dialogue with music delivery. This is evident in his ongoing series titled “EmmaOMG Highlife series”.   5. Twyse Ereme Twyse Ereme is a Nigerian comedian popular on YouTube and Instagram for doing funny comedy skits with only him acting different characters. In 2019, he went from doing trash versions of blown songs to doing proper songs to the point that he released an EP where he featured Dagrin’s brother Trod on “Trippin”.